{"tid":993120,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[macbook撚入］想問下有冇方法唔登入底下熄咗個filevault?","createTime":"2019-01-23T16:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T02:09:36.000Z","uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fad23c55d0a59f419e435359639d2ea41b7543f9","tid":993120,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"事源係 有幾粒制入咗水壞咗<br />\n個密碼有其中一個字所以打唔到(最後啲字用unicode打就打到出黎，但好多位入密碼都唔比用Unicode/Copy&amp;paste)<br />\n想改過個密碼啦<br />\n咁入咗command r諗住用reset password<br />\n點知冇個宗卷我揀黎reset<br />\n意味住開咗filevault <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試過出返去用磁碟工具果喥熄<br />\n點知都係無得copy&amp;paste<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由果個磁碟工具入面個重設密碼工具（有得paste) 果喥都唔比我reset password<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有咩方法可以改密碼/熄咗個filevault <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f732cec345bbcda36fea6f4ee4e36b42d5230a65","tid":993120,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08f8cb9c22914c3732d0f76b1b5895fe11c4b2a3","tid":993120,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa6ac66296a0fc464f6f388acbda1e96ea91436","tid":993120,"uid":21688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s